凰城酒店十三区 2145.55 平方米，凤凰城酒店员工宿舍 12667.82 平方米。 值得一提的是，凤凰城酒店是碧桂园集团内为数不多的一线城市酒店项目，于 2003 年开业，2017 年重新装修，共 573 间豪华客房，产权独立清晰，证载用途为酒店，有抵押，现状为经营。 38.18 亿元！碧桂园拟转让广州多处酒店、写字楼等资产 | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-dd016565a90877de21500ce06cc32b82_b.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/640782399"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I87aflP3X3Y5eEAMaCTEwNDY3NDEwNiD6krytBjAAOCJADnIJNjQwNzgyMzk5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1706015493.819897", "card_id": "Q_640651630", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "运动中的哪个瞬间让你深刻感受到，「你必须很努力，才能看上去毫不费力」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-3c20d89d7c58bc41aec442a16f957794_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "52 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/640651630"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I87aflP3X3Y5eEAMaCTEwNDY0NTA3MyCcqLitBjAAOEBAD3IJNjQwNjUxNjMweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1706015493.821035", "card_id": "Q_639819312", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 39}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "同一只猫咪在不同照片里，颜值差异可以有多大？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-8ed3507cfa560244c2137a8f9b194d58_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "51 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/639819312"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I87aflP3X3Y5eEAMaCTEwNDQ2MDE3MCC815mtBjAAODFAEHIJN